(1) Eskina Banawa (comprising the satellite market, Gullas Compound up to corner Suzara Street all along V. Rama Avenue);

(2) Verano Compound I;

(3) Verano Compound II;

(4) Falek Compound and Sundance Hills;

(5) Damiana's Compound;

